"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"1/ [$based](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24based&src=cashtag_click) is an aesthetic community, art in its primary function: to produce pleasure. The [$based](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24based&src=cashtag_click) market cap is just one metric to measure this commonly shared pleasure.\\n\\n2/ Just as the development of science is largely the result of the work of anonymous artisans, the development of [$based](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24based&src=cashtag_click) is the result of a multitude of anonymous ghouls solving the practical problems of rover deployment.\\n\\n3/ [$based](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24based&src=cashtag_click) is to [#DEFI](https://twitter.com/hashtag/DEFI?src=hashtag_click) what artisan glassmakers have been to astronomy: a history of engineers and illiterate artists.\\n\\n4/ [$based](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24based&src=cashtag_click) is an \\\"Apocalypse of Truth\\\", cause [$based](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24based&src=cashtag_click) is like your buggy TV. It reveals the internal workings of the device and shows new possibilities through this BUG.\\n\\n5/ When an old TV's bug, it makes a glitch, so you understand better how a CRT works. [$Based](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24Based&src=cashtag_click) is like this phenomenon, but for [#DEFI](https://twitter.com/hashtag/DEFI?src=hashtag_click).\\n\\n6/ [$based](https://twitter.com/search?q=%24based&src=cashtag_click) is a [#DEFI](https://twitter.com/hashtag/DEFI?src=hashtag_click) Bug\",\"timestamp\":1634128346,\"title\":\"$Based Manifesto\"},\"digest\":\"JPsRT3jTsaRPTrC7vRRoBQan239Zu6Av53R5bI42Wzs\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xeC637985e0afe64700fAAb8758b1119125175Cee\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"uhDoADu_KHj0_Y5d6D7NTIEE7VvbT34RP84G6mrQwwM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"DA5id9ETtazUu_n8MqggDEEk0K_XXR6ww1YQ1gTi4Zc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"dcbkeN1LrnumeVG6